summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 14W, page 59, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Kilbourne's Addition, West 42 ft. of Lots 1, 2 and 3, Block 101, located on the south side of No. 56th St. east of alley between Kensington Pl. and Kirkwood Pl., as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
